      • mountDeviceSetParamUART

        protected void mountDeviceSetParamUART(int bps,
                                       int dataBits,
                                       int stopBits,
                                       int parity,
                                       int flowCtrl,
                                       int state)
        Set the interface of UART parameters
        参数:
        bps - Baudrate 0: 9600 1:14400 2:19200 3:38400 4:57600 5:115200
        dataBits - Data bits 0:8bits 1:9bits
        stopBits - Stop bits 0:1bits 1:2bits
        parity - Verify 0:No verification 1: odd parity check2:even parity check
        flowCtrl - Fluid control0:No fluid control 1:RTS is effective 2:CTS is effective 3:RTS和CTS are effective at the same time.
        state -

      • mountDeviceSetParamCAN

        protected void mountDeviceSetParamCAN(int bps,
                                      int mode,
                                      int state)
        Set the interface of CAN parameters
        参数:
        bps - Mode 0:Normal mode 1:Silent mode 2:loopback mode 3:Silent loopback mode.
        mode - Baudrate setting 0:5k 1:10k 2:20k 3:50k 4:100k 5:125k 6:250k 7:500k 8:800k 9:1000k
        state - pay close attention to this when you return. There is no need to care when you set up. 0:query successfully 1:query timeout

      • mountDeviceSendDataCAN

        protected void mountDeviceSendDataCAN(int type,
                                      int format,
                                      int id,
                                      byte[] data,
                                      int len,
                                      int encryption)
        Send the data of CAN
        参数:
        type - //ID type 0:Standard ID 1:Extend ID
        format - // Frame format 0:Data frame 1:Remote frame
        id - // Frame id bit0~bit28bits is effective.bit0~bit10 is the Standard frame. bit11~bit28 is the extend frame.
        data - //Transmitted-data
        len - // The length of data
        encryption - //0:No Encryption 1:xxTea Encryption 2:RSA Encryption
